{"text_id":200459,"tokens":["ADHD",","," or"," Attention"," Deficit"," Hyper","activity"," Disorder",","," is"," a"," neuro","developmental"," disorder"," that"," affects"," a"," child","'","s"," ability"," to"," focus",","," control"," impulses",","," and"," manage"," behavior","."," A"," child"," with"," ADHD"," may"," struggle"," to"," follow"," instructions",","," complete"," tasks",","," and"," communicate"," effectively",","," which"," can"," be"," challenging"," for"," both"," the"," child"," and"," their"," parents",".","\n","If"," you"," are"," a"," parent"," of"," a"," child"," with"," ADHD",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," keep"," in"," mind"," that"," in"," no"," way"," or"," form"," is"," your"," child"," stupid"," or"," insane","."," ADHD"," is"," a"," medical"," condition",","," and"," with"," the"," right"," support"," and"," management",","," your"," child"," can"," lead"," a"," happy"," and"," successful"," life",".","\n","In"," this"," article",","," we"," will"," provide"," you"," with"," some"," practical"," tips"," on"," how"," to"," deal"," with"," having"," a"," child"," with"," ADHD",".","\n","1","."," Educate"," yourself",".","\n","The"," first"," step"," in"," dealing"," with"," ADHD"," is"," to"," educate"," yourself"," about"," the"," condition","."," Learn"," about"," the"," symptoms",","," causes",","," and"," treatment"," options"," available","."," There"," are"," many"," resources"," available"," online",","," in"," books",","," and"," through"," support"," groups"," that"," can"," provide"," you"," with"," the"," information"," you"," need",".","\n","2","."," Get"," your"," child"," diagnosed"," by"," a"," doctor"," if"," they"," haven","'","t"," been"," already",".","\n","If"," you"," suspect"," that"," your"," child"," may"," have"," ADHD",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," get"," them"," evaluated"," by"," a"," doctor","."," A"," diagnosis"," can"," help"," you"," understand"," your"," child","'","s"," behavior"," and"," provide"," them"," with"," the"," appropriate"," treatment"," and"," support",".","\n","3","."," Ask"," your"," pediatrician"," about"," your"," child","'","s"," diet",".","\n","Research"," has"," shown"," that"," certain"," foods"," can"," exacerbate"," ADHD"," symptoms","."," Talk"," to"," your"," pediatrician"," about"," your"," child","'","s"," diet"," to"," see"," if"," there"," are"," any"," changes"," you"," can"," make"," to"," help"," manage"," their"," symptoms",".","\n","4","."," Make"," sure"," that"," both"," you"," and"," your"," child"," are"," educated"," about"," ADHD"," and"," your"," treatment"," options",".","\n","It"," is"," important"," for"," both"," you"," and"," your"," child"," to"," understand"," what"," ADHD"," is"," and"," how"," it"," affects"," them","."," Talk"," to"," your"," child"," about"," their"," condition",","," and"," involve"," them"," in"," the"," process"," of"," finding"," the"," right"," treatment"," options",".","\n","5","."," Attend"," support"," groups",".","\n","Support"," groups"," can"," provide"," you"," and"," your"," child"," with"," a"," safe"," and"," supportive"," environment"," where"," you"," can"," share"," your"," experiences"," and"," learn"," from"," others","."," There"," are"," many"," online"," and"," in","-","person"," support"," groups"," available"," that"," cater"," specifically"," to"," parents"," of"," children"," with"," ADHD",".","\n","6","."," Attend"," parenting"," skills"," training",".","\n","Parenting"," skills"," training"," can"," help"," you"," develop"," effective"," parenting"," techniques"," to"," manage"," your"," child","'","s"," behavior","."," This"," training"," can"," teach"," you"," how"," to"," communicate"," better"," with"," your"," child",","," set"," limits",","," and"," provide"," positive"," feedback",".","\n","7","."," Provide"," positive"," feedback"," for"," the"," behavior"," you"," want"," to"," encourage"," and"," ignore"," behavior"," you"," want"," to"," discourage",".","\n","Positive"," reinforcement"," can"," be"," a"," powerful"," tool"," in"," managing"," your"," child","'","s"," behavior","."," Praise"," your"," child"," when"," they"," exhibit"," good"," behavior",","," and"," ignore"," behavior"," that"," you"," want"," to"," discourage",".","\n","8","."," Be"," clear"," and"," consistent"," when"," communicating"," the"," rules"," to"," your"," child",".","\n","Children"," with"," ADHD"," can"," often"," struggle"," with"," following"," rules","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," be"," clear"," and"," consistent"," when"," communicating"," the"," rules"," to"," your"," child","."," Use"," simple"," language"," and"," repeat"," the"," rules"," often",".","\n","9","."," Engage"," in"," pleasant"," or"," relaxing"," activities"," with"," your"," child",".","\n","Eng","aging"," in"," pleasant"," or"," relaxing"," activities"," with"," your"," child"," can"," help"," them"," manage"," their"," symptoms","."," Activities"," such"," as"," coloring",","," painting",","," or"," playing"," outside"," can"," help"," your"," child"," relax"," and"," focus",".","\n","1","0","."," Help"," your"," child"," discover"," what"," they"," do"," well",".","\n","Children"," with"," ADHD"," often"," struggle"," with"," low"," self","-","esteem","."," Help"," your"," child"," discover"," what"," they"," do"," well",","," and"," encourage"," them"," to"," pursue"," their"," strengths",".","\n","1","1","."," Be"," positive"," and"," praise"," your"," child","'","s"," good"," points",".","\n","Children"," with"," ADHD"," need"," positive"," reinforcement"," to"," feel"," good"," about"," themselves","."," Praise"," your"," child"," for"," their"," accomplishments",","," and"," focus"," on"," their"," good"," points",".","\n","1","2","."," Res","truct","ure"," situations"," so"," that"," they"," are"," more"," manageable"," for"," someone"," with"," ADHD",".","\n","Res","truct","ure"," situations"," to"," make"," them"," more"," manageable"," for"," your"," child"," with"," ADHD","."," This"," can"," include"," breaking"," tasks"," into"," smaller"," steps",","," providing"," visual"," aids",","," and"," minimizing"," distractions",".","\n","1","3","."," Look"," into"," getting"," an"," ADD"," coach"," for"," your"," child",".","\n","An"," ADD"," coach"," can"," help"," your"," child"," manage"," their"," symptoms"," and"," develop"," effective"," strategies"," for"," managing"," their"," behavior","."," Look"," for"," a"," coach"," who"," is"," experienced"," in"," working"," with"," children"," with"," ADHD",".","\n","1","4","."," Consider"," social"," skills"," training"," as"," this"," may"," teach"," your"," child"," behaviors"," which"," will"," help"," them"," develop"," and"," maintain"," social"," relationships",".","\n","Social"," skills"," training"," can"," help"," your"," child"," develop"," the"," skills"," they"," need"," to"," build"," and"," maintain"," social"," relationships","."," Look"," for"," a"," program"," that"," is"," tailored"," specifically"," to"," children"," with"," ADHD",".","\n","1","5","."," Create"," a"," daily"," schedule"," and"," keep"," the"," same"," daily"," routine"," from"," wake","-","up"," time"," to"," bedtime",".","\n","Children"," with"," ADHD"," thrive"," on"," routine","."," Create"," a"," daily"," schedule"," and"," stick"," to"," it"," as"," much"," as"," possible","."," This"," can"," help"," your"," child"," feel"," more"," organized"," and"," reduce"," their"," anxiety",".","\n","1","6","."," Limit"," TV"," time",".","\n","Excessive"," screen"," time"," can"," exacerbate"," ADHD"," symptoms","."," Limit"," your"," child","'","s"," TV"," time",","," and"," encourage"," them"," to"," engage"," in"," other"," activities",".","\n","1","7","."," Ask"," your"," child","'","s"," school"," to"," see"," if"," your"," child"," is"," eligible"," for"," special"," education"," services",".","\n","Your"," child"," may"," be"," eligible"," for"," special"," education"," services"," at"," school","."," Talk"," to"," your"," child","'","s"," teacher"," or"," school"," counselor"," to"," find"," out"," what"," options"," are"," available",".","\n","Dealing"," with"," having"," a"," child"," with"," ADHD"," can"],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}